  <title>libogg-&libogg-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The libogg package contains the Ogg file structure. This is useful for
      creating (encoding) or playing (decoding) a single physical bit stream.
    </para>

